data.description: Walk right in to your beautifully updated dream home with beautiful lake views with plenty of room for everyone.  This magnificent home boasts 3 large bedrooms, with a potential 4th bedroom in the finished basement, along with 3 full updated bathrooms. As soon as you pull into the oversized driveway with plenty of room to park all of your cars, you will admire the beautifully maintained property.  From the moment you walk through the front door you will not be disappointed. The first floor features a beautiful kitchen which offers an eat-in kitchen and connects to the living room.  Off of the living room you will find a large first floor bedroom, and also a first-floor full bathroom and laundry room.  The second floor features an amazing primary bedroom with large walk-in closet and en suite bathroom with dual vanities.  The basement offers plenty of storage space, and a playroom or possible 4th bedroom if needed.  Be sure to check this amazing home out as you will not be disappointed!
